ver 01
23 December 2021

This strategy using :
- 3 EMA period 50, 100, 200
- stochastic RSI slow

Long Cond :
- Stochastic RSI cross below 20
- EMA 50 > 100 > 200

Short Cond :
- Stochastic RSI cross above 80
- EMA 50 < 100 < 200

Sleeping Mode
- EMA 50 between EMA 100 & EMA 200
